<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - CIENA rated hold.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - CIENA rated hold.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- SoundView Financial Group said analyst Kevin Slocum initiated coverage of CIENA Corp with short- and long-term hold ratings.</p>
<p>-- Set earnings per share estimates of $0.62 for fiscal 1997 and $0.80 for fiscal 1998.</p>
<p>-- The stock was off 1-7/8 to 29-1/2.</p>
